race.description: Tatts Hotel Great Northern Inverell Cup
race.comment: VORACIOUS (4) raced on the speed and kept going to score by a nose last time out over 1350m at Doomben. Only needs to hold his form to prove hard to beat. SATAY CHICKEN (13) has been good in his two runs back and should be hitting his straps now. Will relish the rise in trip and should be taking strong strides late. ZAMBORGHINI (14) hasn't won for a long time but lines up well for this off 53 days, switching to the Hatch stable and bringing solid Victorian form. Draws well and gets in light with the claim. Can give this a big shake. MYSTERY LAD (3) progressed nicely last time out to finish a close second at Tamworth. A similar effort here has him in the finish again. Last start winner NIGHT FIGHTER (11) also deserves following up from the gun draw.
